citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately
9:15AM on 22-SEPT-2023.
I went to the address provided in the customer's application for registration and was told the registrant did not live at this
address. I then tried to call the number provided by the customer in his application for registration. The person answering
the phone confirmed I dialed the number provided in the customer's application but stated that they did not know this
individual.
End Section

narrative:
2.126(b) 
   
Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries. 
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at approximately 
9:15AM on 22-SEPT-2023. 
I went to the address provided in the customer's application for registration and was told the registrant did not live at this 
address. I then tried to call the number provided by the customer in his application for registration. The person answering 
the phone confirmed I dialed the number provided in the customer's application but stated that they did not know this 
individual. 
 
 
End Section
